  <SanguophageMeetingHost.questContentRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>sanguophagesArriveLetterLabel->赫血种抵达</li>
    <li>sanguophagesArriveLetterText->[sanguophageCount]个赫血种从[map_definite]不同方向抵达，他们将在殖民地会面并进行协商。</li>
    <li>argumentLetterLabel->赫血种争执</li>
